Description: TokenShield unified tokenization service
 TokenShield is a PCI compliance gateway demonstrating credit card
 tokenization using modern proxy technologies. The unified service
 provides HTTP tokenization, ICAP detokenization, and a management
 REST API.
 .
 This package contains the unified tokenizer service that handles:
  - HTTP tokenization server (port 8080)
  - ICAP detokenization server (port 1344)
  - REST management API (port 8090)
  - KEK/DEK encryption support
  - Configurable token formats